text: Případ Z-8 is a 1948 Czechoslovak drama film, directed by Miroslav Cikán. It stars Josef Bek, Milica Kolofiková, and Jiřina Petrovická. ==References== ==External links== *Případ Z-8 at the Internet Movie Database Category:1948 films Category:Czechoslovak films Category:Czechoslovak drama films Category:1948 drama films Category:Films directed by Miroslav Cikán Category:Czech films Category:Czechoslovak black-and-white films
